   "source": "<ROUTINE BARK-CONTINUES ()\n\t <TELL CR \"The barking on the \" D ,WTK\n\t\t  \" continues for a few moments\">\n\t <COND (<ZERO? ,MLIVES>\n\t\t<TELL \". Then you hear a sharp \">\n\t\t<ITALICIZE \"crack,\">\n\t\t<TELL \" and the barking stops.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)>\n\t <TELL \", then dies away.\" CR>\n\t <RTRUE>>"
