   "source": "<ROUTINE DOG-ALERT ()\n\t <TELL CR\n\"\\\"Nice puppy,\\\" you mumble.|\n|\nThe 110-pound \\\"puppy\\\" strains against its chain, opens its toothy maw and starts\">\n\t <AKC>\n\t <COND (<HEAR-BAKER?>\n\t\t<HEAR-BARKING>)>\n\t <TELL CR\n\"You stumble backwards to hide as the \" D ,SLIGHT\n\" sweeps across the road.\" CR>\n\t <HOLD-IT>\n\t <KINDA-SPY>\n\t <SURROUNDED>\n\t <RTRUE>>"
