   "source": "<ROUTINE INTO-CORRUPTION (\"OPTIONAL\" (TOUCH? <>))\n\t <MOVE ,HEAP ,SBOG>\n\t <REMOVE ,GLOWING-LOG>\n\t <MOVE ,SHARD ,SBOG>\n\t <SETG P-IT-OBJECT ,SHARD>\n\t <TELL \"into a \" D ,HEAP>\n\t <COND (<T? .TOUCH?>\n\t\t<TELL \" when you try to move it\">)>\n\t <TELL \". Only a big \" D ,SHARD \" of wood remains.\" CR>\n\t <RTRUE>>"
