   "source": "<ROUTINE MUNG-LAMP ()\n\t <COND (<IS? ,LAMP ,CHILLY>\n\t\t<TELL \"This has little effect on the broken \"\n\t\t      D ,LAMP ,PERIOD>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)>\n\t <MAKE ,LAMP ,CHILLY>\n\t <SETG BEAM 0>\n\t <TELL CTHE ,LAMP \" snaps with a loud \">\n\t <COND (<IS? ,LAMP ,LIGHTED>\n\t\t<ITALICIZE \"crack\">\n\t\t<TELL \" and goes out.\" CR>\n\t\t<KILL-LAMP>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)>\n\t <ITALICIZE \"crack.\">\n\t <CRLF>\n\t <RTRUE>>"
