   "source": "<ROUTINE TURN-ON-LAMP ()\n\t <COND (<IS? ,LAMP ,SHADOWY>\n\t\t<TELL CTHE ,LAMP \"'s switch is already turned on.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)>\n\t <MAKE ,LAMP ,SHADOWY>\n\t <ITALICIZE \"Click.\">\n\t <TELL \" The \">\n\t <COND (<OR <ZERO? ,BEAM>\n\t\t    <IS? ,LAMP ,CHILLY>>\n\t\t<COND (<T? ,BEAM>\n\t\t       <TELL \"broken \">)>\n\t\t<TELL D ,LAMP \" doesn't respond.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)>\n\t <QUEUE I-HARDHAT -1>\n\t <MAKE ,LAMP ,LIGHTED>\n\t <TELL D ,LAMP \" emits a warm, yellow beam.\" CR>\n\t <COND (<ZERO? ,LIT?>\n\t\t<SETG LIT? T>\n\t\t<SETG OLD-HERE <>>\n\t\t<CRLF>\n\t\t<V-LOOK>)>\n\t <RTRUE>>"
