   "source": "<ROUTINE DESCRIBE-PEDESTAL (\"OPTIONAL\" (CONTEXT <>))\n\t <COND (<NOT <EQUAL? .CONTEXT ,M-OBJDESC>>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>\n\t <TELL \"The biggest book you've ever seen lies open on a \"\n\t       D ,PEDESTAL \" in the \" D ,CORNER \".\">\n\t <RTRUE>>"
