   "source": "<ROUTINE HANDLE-BOOK? ()\n\t <COND (<THIS-PRSI?>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (<VERB? TOUCH KISS SQUEEZE>\n\t\t<TELL CTHE ,PAGES \" feel smooth and creamy.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? SMELL>\n\t\t<TELL \"The dusty \" D ,PAGES \" make you sneeze.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? OPEN OPEN-WITH UNFOLD>\n\t\t<TELL CTHE ,TOME \" is already open.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? CLOSE FOLD>\n\t\t<TELEPHONE>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>>"
