   "value": "<PTABLE <LTABLE 2 \" croak\" \" squawk\" \" screeche\" \" say\" \" mutter\"> <LTABLE 2 \"Milk and honey\" \"Milk and honey, fresh whole lizard\" \"Fresh whole lizard\" \"Killed in the light of a crescent moon\" \"Crescent moon\" \"Mix 'em with a pinch o' garlic\" \"Then stand back! 'Cause it go BOOM\" \"It go BOOM\"> <LTABLE 2 \" blinks at you\" \" makes a croaking sound\" \" wiggles its head\" \" whistles\" \" ruffles its feathers\" \" scratches an itchy wing\" \" eyes you suspiciously\" \" cranes its neck\" \" beats its wings\" \" sharpens its beak\">>"
